            <title><![CDATA[下午察：童话大王郑渊洁过度维权？]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media"><img class="img-fluid lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2023/04/19/Screenshot1_1.jpg?VersionId=QMbjZxDvgnR5dH8bXQacsZIoLVBMBfkU&amp;itok=64eQjAaF" title="中国童话大王郑渊洁笔下经典角色舒克和贝塔。（互联网）" alt="中国童话大王郑渊洁笔下经典角色舒克和贝塔。（互联网）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/articles/2023/04/19/Screenshot1_1.jpg?VersionId=QMbjZxDvgnR5dH8bXQacsZIoLVBMBfkU&amp;itok=64eQjAaF" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></div>
